            "body": "I think #36457 resolves this, although the `CursorMoved` autocommand fired by extui's `cmdline.lua` may result in zombie match IDs in the repro here. Updating `add_hl()` like so resolves that:\n```lua\nlocal add_hl = vim.schedule_wrap(function()\n  remove_hl()\n  cur_match = vim.fn.matchadd('Red', [[\\k*\\%#\\k*]])\nend)\n```\n\nHopefully we'll have a matchparen.lua that can be called without having to fire an autocommand in the futureðŸ˜­ (seems like that is the case in #31861ðŸ¥³).",
